data.description: Welcome to this charming single-level home that combines modern comfort with functionality! This property offers 4 beds, 2 baths, and an RV gate. The interior features tile flooring, designer paint, and vaulted ceilings, adding to the spacious feel. You'll love the sizable living room showcasing an entertainment niche and pre-wired surround sound, perfectly designed for movie nights. The eat-in kitchen comes with recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, granite counters, tile backsplash, and sliding glass doors leading to the back patio. Discover the primary bedroom boasting a walk-in closet, direct outdoor access, and a bathroom with dual sinks. The large backyard includes a relaxing covered patio and a convenient storage shed. Hurry! Don't waste time!
